				<div id="head-tag">	




	
				


	
				
																					

				
	</div>
				<h1 id="headline" class="eza-title">
											
Coronavirus test: What makes a good leader in times of crisis?									</h1>
			</div>
		</div>

		
				<div class="row">
			<div class="editor-intro small-centered eza-body small-12 medium-11">
				<h2 class="title text-center">Why We Wrote This</h2>
				<div>
					
<p>When faced with uncertainty, people look to leadership for information, reassurance, and guidance.&nbsp;Faced with a global pandemic, a wide range of leaders are stepping up to fill those roles in different ways.</p>				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
				<article id="story-content">
			
